{
  "texts": [
    "The output of the convolutional operation is referred to as feature maps.",
    "Fig. 1 illustrates the process of applying convolutional operation to a 6 × 6 image data.",
    "After the convolutional operation, the output is passed to the pooling layer for further processing.",
    "In the CNN architecture, there is no direct connection allowing information to flow from the next layer back to the previous layer.",
    "This implies that there is no direct communication between the layers."
  ]
}